r\u00f8ndelag og ogs\u00e5 andre plasser i Trondheim b\u00f8r tenke seg om og lese flere studier p\u00e5 ungdom som trenger snus ogs\u00e5 p\u00e5 skolen.", "Jeg er veldig sikker p\u00e5 at elevene som snuser kommer til \u00e5 gj\u00f8re det bedre p\u00e5 skolen dersom snus blir lovlig. Og ikke minst minske anmerkningene hos disse elevene.", "S\u00e5 v\u00e6r s\u00e5 snill, tenk dere om.", "Nina Christine Lund (16)"]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "meninger"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "meninger|snakkut"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "fef581d0d1da5113ddcd0c1805dcbeff03d521f4f991337521d6eac98efc7f6e"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2015-09-01T12:59:34.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Hvorfor er det ikke lov \u00e5 snuse p\u00e5 videreg\u00e5ende skole?"}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2120152.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/snus-seksjon"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/1332c22301e93447ab973c98ce1640e7f84a7789.jpg?5908d3f8"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": ["Snus p\u00e5 skolen -adressa.no", "Avhengig", "Tenk dere om"]}, {"field": "id", "value": "1332c22301e93447ab973c98ce1640e7f84a7789"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["meninger", "snakk ut", "leder"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "meninger,snakk ut,leder"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["meninger", "snakkut"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "education"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["snus", "videreg\u00e5ende skole", "skole"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["s\u00f8r-tr\u00f8ndelag", "trondheim"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-taxonomy", "value": ["meninger", "meninger/snakkut"]}, {"field": "og-image", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article2120152.ece5/ALTERNATES/w980-default/snus-seksjo